{"word":"G1300 - διατελέω - diateléō - dee-at-el-eh'-o - Continue","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">διατελέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">diateléō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">dee-at-el-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Continue</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - தொடர்ந்திரு"},{"paragraph":"to bring thoroughly to an end, accomplish"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1223 - διά - diá - dee-ah'/1223\">G1223</a> and <a href=\"#/G5055 - τελέω - teléō - tel-eh'-o/5055\">G5055</a>; to <i>accomplish thoroughly</i>, that is, (subjectively) to <i>persist:</i> - continue.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}